{
  "stem": "26447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We went to ask something food for us, and we bring for him something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Now, hungry, always hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Now, we was-- when you see us in that time, you will never see what it's people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It's like animals.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We didn't shave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We didn't cut our hair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Everything is dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The hand-- you cannot see some clear places on the hand, on the face.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Now, all the winter time we was in the hole in the ground.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Then, in spring, when the water come out-- the underground water-- become up and up and we cannot stay more.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Then we get out from the place, from the holes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we begin-- oh, it's become more-- the climate, it was better.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "No frost-- frozen more.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And we stay in forest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Never we was anywhere asleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "You find places if you know how it's going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Winter time, the people in the villages, they make hay for the animals.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "In summer time, you cannot come in the places because it's a lot of water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "You cannot take the leave that's on the ground and in the forest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Then, only winter time, they pick up these.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We was going into sleep, sleep-- how-- it will be but sometime, you want to sleep.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "We came to the-- where is the hay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "We come inside and we stay for a night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "In morning, we get up and run in another place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we stay in the ground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The snow-- we clean up the snow and put a little-- from the woods-- leaves or what.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we put-- he take off his jacket, and I take off his jacket, and we stay back to back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in this position, we were sleeping, maybe-- how in the frost, how in the cool, how you can sleep?",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
